A FrameNet-based API to GF Resource Grammar Library

Publications:

  • Extracting a bilingual semantic grammar from FrameNet-annotated corpora
    Proceedings of the 9th International Language Resources and Evaluation Conference (LREC), 2014, pp. 2466-2473
  • Controlled Natural Language Generation from a Multilingual FrameNet-based Grammar
    Proceedings of the 4th Workshop on Controlled Natural Language (CNL), 2014 (to appear)

Source code: comming soon...

Note: for browsing the API docummentation (below), please, use Chrome if possible.

Abandonment

  • Abandonment_Act_V2 : Agent_NP → Theme_NP → V2 → Clause
    • Eng: <Agent>[The council] [ABANDONED] <Theme>[its plans to widen the highway]

      <Agent>[The council] <Time>[later] [ABANDONED] <Theme>[its plans to widen the highway] and the reversion passed to the first defendants , who were not a highway authority .

      • abandon_V2

        <Agent>[The council] [ABANDONED] <Theme>[its plans to widen the highway]

      • forget_V2

        <Agent>[she] [FORGOT] <Theme>[her hairbrush]

    • Swe: <Agent>[Besättningen på Skandia] tvingades att [ÖVERGE] <Theme>[båten]

      <Agent>[Besättningen på Skandia] tvingades att [ÖVERGE] <Theme>[båten] <Explanation>[på grund av stora skador som gjort den omöjlig att navigera] .

      • glömma_V2

        <Agent>[Läkare] [GLÖMDE KVAR] <Theme>[kompress]

      • lämna_V2

        <Agent>[Jag] har [LÄMNAT] <Theme>[bilen]

      • överge_V2

        <Agent>[Besättningen på Skandia] tvingades att [ÖVERGE] <Theme>[båten]

  • Abandonment_Pass_V2 : Theme_NP → V2 → Clause
    • Eng: <Theme>[Another vehicle] was [ABANDONED]

      <Theme>[Another vehicle] was [ABANDONED] <Place>[at Great Victoria Street] .

      • abandon_V2

        <Theme>[Another vehicle] was [ABANDONED]

    • Swe: <Theme>[väljarna] [LÄMNAS I STICKET]

      På denna punkt anser Kurt Johannesson att <Theme>[väljarna] [LÄMNAS I STICKET] <Event_descriptor>[i årets valrörelse] .
